### Running the Server

```bash
# Build the server
pnpm --filter mcp build

# Run in stdio mode
pnpm --filter mcp start

# Run in SSE mode
pnpm --filter mcp start --transport sse --port 3000

# With MCP Inspector
npx @modelcontextprotocol/inspector pnpm --filter mcp start
```

